<p>You may search your deck even if you know the card is not present as that knowledge is not public (it may be in your hand, etc)</p>
<h4 id="faq33">The Fixer</h4>
<p>Discard the cards from the top of your deck</p>
<h4 id="faq34">Fred Aims</h4>
<p>His trait defines his base influence (as if it were printed in the chip), other modifiers still apply.</p>
